menu "PhoneBlock Dongle"

    config PHONEBLOCK_BASE_URL
        string "PhoneBlock API base URL"
        default "https://phoneblock.net/phoneblock/api"
        help
            Base URL for the PhoneBlock REST API. Endpoints are appended
            as /num/{phone}, /rate, etc.

            Two endpoints exist:
              * https://phoneblock.net/phoneblock/api  — production
              * https://phoneblock.net/pb-test/api     — test instance

            A token is bound to exactly one instance. Tokens generated on
            the test instance only work there, and vice versa. The token
            prefix (pbt_) is the same in both cases.

    config PHONEBLOCK_TOKEN
        string "PhoneBlock Bearer token"
        default ""
        help
            Bearer token used for API authentication. Generate one in the
            PhoneBlock web settings. Starts with "pbt_". Leave empty and
            keep it in sdkconfig.defaults.local (gitignored) instead of
            committing it.

    config PHONEBLOCK_TEST_NUMBER
        string "Test phone number"
        default "030123456"
        help
            Phone number queried at startup to verify the setup. Use the
            PhoneBlock storage format (national: 030..., or 00<cc><num>
            for international, e.g. 0015551234567).

endmenu
